week it's all about taking on big energy companies, both cutting
bills and getting justice for those who've been mistreated. Plus,
are premium bonds worth it and how to fight for your consumer
rights. Watch last week's ( https://www.itv.com/itvplayer/the-martin-lewis-money-show ).

