So do our top fixes comparison ( http://www.msetool.co.uk/redirect/energy_toppicks ) for full
details of how it stacks up for you. The switch-over can be as
quick as 3 weeks (longer for some), so the cheaper price should
kick in soon.

Top Picks (based on typical usage - varies by region)
