The news got it wrong... train self service ticket machines
WON'T tell you cheapest price. ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/split-cheap-train-tickets/ )The
news told us from March train ticket machines will tell you the
cheapest fare. NOT TRUE. 1) They just have to warn you they may
not be cheapest. 2) They ignore split ticketing, which on some
routes halves costs. Use our free Tickety Split tool ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/split-cheap-train-tickets/ ) to
check.

