			<td style="background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 13px; color: #222;" bgcolor="#ffffff">
				<strong>Don't save if you've costly debts</strong>. If you've got both debts and savings, STOP. A &pound;1,000 credit card debt at 18		<br />
		If you're saying &quot;but I need some savings for emergencies&quot;, this is often false logic. Read my <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/savings/pay-off-debts?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=hiya&amp;utm_term=06-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=savings&amp;utm_content=32" style="color: #0047d9;">Repay Debts or Save?</a> guide for full help.</td>
