  <em style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8;"><strong>&quot;I can't believe my old energy provider owed me money. </strong></em><em style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8;"><strong>I rang it, it 'ummed' and 'aahed' a bit, then the lady on the other end  eventually found my old account and it was in credit by &pound;119!&quot; </strong></em> <br />
  - see our <a href="http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/utilities/reclaim-energy-bill-refunds?utm_source=MSE_Newsletter&amp;utm_medium=oneliner-four&amp;utm_term=06-Jan-15-v1&amp;utm_campaign=utilities&amp;utm_content=27" style="color: #0047d9;">Are you owed old energy credit?</a> guide to get your money back.  </p>


	

